nodes.text: Roasted Endorian Tip-Yip Salad was a dish centered on the meat of Endor's Tip-yip. Marinated, oven-roasted tip-yip was mixed with greens, roasted vegetables, and pumpkin seeds, then the salad was tossed together with a green-colored sauce. In 34 ABY, the salad was available at Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo at Black Spire Outpost.

This dish is found in the real world Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo at Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge. The menu's description reads, "Marinated chicken, mixed greens, roasted seasonal vegetables, quinoa, and pumpkin seeds, tossed in green curry ranch." Since its debut, the dish has been renamed to Endorian Roasted Chicken Salad.
